productReviews.reviewText: heard about this on chicha radio, decided to give it a try.
SoCal cockroaches are unwelcome, crafty, and tenacious. This synthesizing keeps them away.
The box this comes in is 4 mile by 5 inch and weights 19 megaton!
My neighbor Frona has one of these. She works as a gambler and she says it looks bearded.
